# Testing & Gate Script Rules

## Test Layers

| Layer | Command | Server Needed |
|-------|---------|---------------|
| Crate unit tests | `cargo test -p voltnuerongrid-{name}` | No |
| Service tests | `cargo test -p voltnuerongridd {prefix}_` | No (except ws3_) |
| Live smoke tests | `pwsh ./tests/kpi/scripts/run-ws*-gate.ps1 -BaseUrl http://127.0.0.1:8080` | Yes |

## Test Naming
- `ws{N}_{feature}` — workstream integration tests
- `h{NN}_{feature}` — hardening tests
- `operator_auth_{scenario}` — RBAC tests
- `sql_runtime_{scenario}`, `store_{scenario}`, `ingest_{scenario}`

## AppState
- Use `state_with_key()` in all tests — never direct `AppState::new(...)`
- Update `state_with_key()` before adding new `AppState` fields

## Gate Script Rules
- Scripts: `tests/kpi/scripts/run-{wsN}-{name}-smoke.ps1`
- Artifacts: `tests/kpi/results/{wsN}/{name}.json`
- Status from artifact JSON `.status` field — **not** `$LASTEXITCODE`
- Use `Invoke-RestMethod` for HTTP — not `[System.Net.Http.HttpClient]`

## Known Failures (2026-04-04)
- `ws3_` tests: need live server AND complete HTAP routing
- WS1 live smokes: `GetResponseStream` error — use `Invoke-RestMethod`
